      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "ZAYYANO (4) is a former Victorian who resumed in stronger at the Gold Coast and needed the outing. His provincial form reads well and he will enjoy the step up to 1650m. Has a handy 2kg claim and the blinkers on again. FIVE OF US (9) has been racing in better Maidens and comes back to this trip off a middle-distance placing at Ipswich. Has trialled solidly at the Gold Coast since and is well placed to feature. BLOOD RED (7) ran a better race when he worked home well and finished 3.5 lengths away over 1690m at Ipswich. He'll be in the finish holding that form. SONIC FLYER (5) will be fitter and will find this more suitable than Eagle Farm and Ipswich. The 1650m is sure to suit. THE MESSIAH (6) will be around the mark off a Grafton 1400m placing.",
